Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:20.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}はじまりのナンバー　夢にとどけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:25.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}平坦な道　探して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}進むことに飽きたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:31.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}叶えても　叶うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:36.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢はなぜこの手で　形を変えてくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:42.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}教えて　どれくらい？　頑張れば辿り着くの…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:48.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}理想につぶれてた　私はもういない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先をリライト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:54.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}掴みたいよ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:02:02.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君と声を重ねて　届けるの　もっと先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ歩けない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}景色　君とみてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:11.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ひとりじゃ進めない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直感を信じて生きてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:17.37,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢の先の New World
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}聞こえていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:24.54,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}この声が終わるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:28.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君に伝え続けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:02.79,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的續集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:06.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}會聽到未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:11.55,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:20.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}送出的開場曲 飛向夢想吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:25.44,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}總是尋找平坦的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.74,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}只會讓我厭倦前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:31.74,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}就算去實現 也只是完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:36.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想為何會因為這隻手改變形態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:42.75,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}請告訴我 還要努力多久才能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:48.05,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}曾經只能仰視理想的我 已經改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}重寫夢想的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:54.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望把握住未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:02:02.10,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我們的聲音重疊 直抵更遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.19,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人走不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:08.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}想和你一同欣賞美景
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:11.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一個人無法前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}希望能追隨直覺活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:17.37,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}夢想前方的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:20.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}你聽清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:24.54,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}直到無法發聲為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:28.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我都會一直為你開口
Comment: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:24.18,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED「STAND BY YOU」------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:29.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by me, you did that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:32.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:42.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}気持ち伝えるのにいつも何故　こんなにも悩み
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:45.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ゆらり揺れている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:52.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}本当は君が好きなのに　うらはらで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:55.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}上手く言えないよ　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:58.42,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}君が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:05.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}目と目合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:10.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}愛の歌　そう唄い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:16.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}君にいつか届くまでね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:19.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}大事にしてたフィーリング
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:21.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全部込めるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:26.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}ちゃんと受け止めてくれるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:31.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}真夜中のラブソングで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:37.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}世界がちょっと変わってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:43.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}そして君とsweetie　2人ぼっち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}100ミリちょっとの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:48.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}隙間埋める
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:49.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}be with you
Comment: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:29.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by me, you did that
Comment: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:32.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Stand by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:42.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}只是表明心意 為什麼讓我如此煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:45.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}總是搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:52.04,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}其實那麼喜歡你 卻言不由衷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:55.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}找不到合適的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.63,0:21:58.42,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}回首身後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.59,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}眼中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:05.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}我們四目相對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:10.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}唱響這首愛之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:16.65,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}希望有一天你能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:19.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}一直珍惜的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:21.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}都包含其中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:26.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}你一定會接受它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:31.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}願這首午夜小情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:37.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}可以讓世界稍微改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:43.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}然後與你甜甜蜜蜜 二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:45.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}十多公分的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:48.06,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}全都被填滿
Comment: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:49.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,be with you
